articles.title: No further sightings of crocodile at Sentosa; suspension of water activities lifted
articles.content: This caused concern and disappointment among beachgoers. SDC has since been conducting daily surveillance and coordinated patrols with the National Parks Board (NParks), said an SDC spokesperson. "Based on the current assessment, water activities, including swimming, kayaking and organised events, can resume with immediate effect," the spokesperson added

articles.title: 25-year-old man arrested for Pokemon trading cards scam with losses totalling $135k
articles.content: In a media release on Friday (Feb 6) evening, the police said they received 35 reports from victims since October 2025, with losses amounting over $135,000. He will be charged in court for cheating on Saturday. The police urged the public to be careful when making online purchases
